{"tid":1708374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[1112行動］黎明行動2.0 - 淺黃向零成本超合作運動","createTime":"2019-11-11T14:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T18:09:41.000Z","uid":106796,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0c638b339488aa4926e504a6fce1c9e512977cc6","tid":1708374,"uid":106796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"今日各位手足都應該知今日黎明行動問題出左係邊，黨鐵全線朝早暢通無阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，小弟呼籲各位和理非聽朝700準時落到各區黨鐵站有上無落，特別要係黨鐵各大重要交通交匯位置來回超合作地乘搭黨鐵返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各大黨鐵返工春袋位：<br />\n將軍澳線：調景嶺《》北角<br />\n觀塘線：觀塘《》油麻地<br />\n港島線：鰂魚涌《》中環<br />\n荃灣線：荔景《》中環<br />\n東鐵線：紅磡《》火炭<br />\n<br />\n以上為建議路線，開放討論<br />\n<br />\n經過今日一役相信大家都好攰，聽朝又7點要返工一定好易訓著搭過龍，但大家都一定會準時落去搭黨鐵返工做良好市民，特別係今日無罷工，無出黎個班，你地識聽朝點做啦，聽朝7點我要睇到班港豬同藍屍上唔撚到黨鐵係到屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3550d568c9fe997b85f12e1dfc72ebbd5eba81","tid":1708374,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"［全民罷工妙計］繁忙時間要引狗衝入港鐵站向返工人士施襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb11f14a3df6892dd9f0e4e147702f6dd98612e0","tid":1708374,"uid":106796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:37:44.000Z","msg":"甴近平比所有和理非睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b45b0d695eb83bb1faacf9a19641dfbfa8d986","tid":1708374,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n今日警察攻入教堂打人<br />\nNY Times 記者rt 左<br />\n推畀國際知！！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pekingmike/status/1193893990128652288?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%